        </a>
    </section>

    <section class="sos-section">
        <div class="sos-content">
            <div class="sos-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="sos-text">
                <h2>Emergency Help – We’re Here for You!</h2>
                <p>In times of crisis, every second counts. Trust our rapid response team to provide the immediate assistance you need. Don’t wait – your safety is our priority.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="sos-call-btn">
            <img src="assets/sos2.png" alt="sos"> Connect
        </button>
    </section>

    <h3>Immediate Action</h3>

    <section class="emergency-container">
        <div class="video-section">
            <iframe 
                width="100%" 
                height="100%" 
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2PngCv7NjaI?si=EvBdoBuVLZ2pcD2_" 
                title="Emergency Video" 
                frameborder="0" 
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
                allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="steps-section">
            <h6 class="caption">CPR - Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation</h6>
            <div class="step" data-step="1">
                <img src="assets/cpr1.jpg" alt="Step 1" class="step-img">
                <p>Check for responsiveness and call emergency services if unresponsive.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step" data-step="2">
                <img src="assets/cpr2.jpg" alt="Step 2" class="step-img">
                <p>Start chest compressions if there is no pulse.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step" data-step="3">
                <img src="assets/cpr3.png" alt="Step 3" class="step-img">
                <p>Continue CPR until help arrives or the person regains consciousness.</p>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="emergency-container2">
        <div class="steps-section2">
            <div class="steps-left">
                <h6 class="caption">Heimlich Maneuver</h6>
                <div class="step-right">
                    <img src="/assets/maneuever1.jpg" alt="Step 1" class="step-image">
                    <p>Stand behind the person and wrap your arms around their waist.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-right">
                    <img src="/assets/Screenshot 2024-11-06 222634.png" alt="Step 2" class="step-image">
                    <p>Make a fist with one hand and place it just above their navel.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-right">
                    <img src="/assets/maneuever3.jpg" alt="Step 3" class="step-image">
                    <p>Grasp your fist with the other hand and thrust it inward and upward.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-right">
                    <img src="/assets/maneuver4.jpg" alt="Step 4" class="step-image">
                    <p>For Children - Lay the child face down, Give five quick, firm back blows</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="video-right">
                <iframe width="100%" height="100%" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7CgtIgSyAiU?si=DtHxG0GPtAweDG4R"
                    title="Heimlich Maneuver" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="emergency-container">
        <div class="video-section">
            <iframe 
                width="100%" 
                height="100%" 
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0xubzGiAjEU?si=XoelCpia2UuurQV0" 
                title="Emergency Video" 
                frameborder="0" 
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
                allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="steps-section">
            <h6 class="caption">Heartstroke</h6>
            <div class="step" data-step="1">
                <img src="assets/heat1.webp" alt="Step 1" class="step-img">
                <p>Move the person to a cool, shaded place.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step" data-step="2">
                <img src="assets/heat3.webp" alt="Step 2" class="step-img">
                <p>Apply cool, wet cloths to the skin, or sponge with water.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step" data-step="3">
                <img src="assets/heat2.webp" alt="Step 3" class="step-img">
                <p>Offer sips of water if the person is alert.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step" data-step="3">
                <img src="assets/sos2.png" alt="Step 3" class="step-img">
                <p>Monitor for signs of improvement or worsening symptoms.</p>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="emergency-container2">
        <div class="steps-section2">
            <div class="steps-left">
                <h6 class="caption">Bleeding Control</h6>
                <div class="step-right">
                    <img src="/assets/maneuever1.jpg" alt="Step 1" class="step-image">
                    <p>Apply direct pressure to the wound with a clean cloth.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-right">
                    <img src="/assets/Screenshot 2024-11-06 222634.png" alt="Step 2" class="step-image">
                    <p>Elevate the injured area above heart level if possible.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-right">
                    <img src="/assets/maneuever3.jpg" alt="Step 3" class="step-image">
                    <p>Wrap the wound firmly with a bandage, but not too tight.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-right">
                    <img src="/assets/maneuver4.jpg" alt="Step 4" class="step-image">
                    <p>Use a tourniquet if bleeding is severe and unmanageable.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="video-right">
                <iframe width="100%" height="100%" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gMMfl0wCxHM?si=J-apgnxpaA3Zn_Ga"
                    title="Heimlich Maneuver" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>



